						               													<description>Blood Mansion is a Murder Mystery Card game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players take turns drawing, stealing and discarding cards all in an attempt to discover who is the actual killer.&amp;#10;The deck is made up of: Murder Cards which reveal the murder scene and weapon used. Action cards which help you gain information and screw up your opponents attempts to solve the crime. Guilt cards that help convict a suspect. Weapon cards which of only one can be the actual weapon each game. Suspect cards, most of which are Red Herrings (i.e. false leads)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game gets more and more intense with each card you draw because fewer cards left in the deck means a greater chance of solving the Murder for yourself or that someone else is about to beat you to the punch. A certain amount of bluffing and deduction is part of the success to winning the game.&amp;#10;Fully funded on Kickstarter in July 2017 the game currently is the manufacturing phase at Panda Games. For more information go to www.BloodMansion.com&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
